import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { Nav, NavDropdown, Dropdown } from 'react-bootstrap';
import '../styles/CategoryMenu.css';

class CatagoryMenu extends Component {

	render() {
		return (
			<Nav justify defaultActiveKey="/home" as="ul" className="itemDropnList">
				<Nav.Item as="li">
					<Nav.Link href="/home">Clothing</Nav.Link>

				</Nav.Item>
				<Nav.Item as="li">
					<Nav.Link eventKey="link-1">Sportwear</Nav.Link>
				</Nav.Item>
				<Nav.Item as="li">
					<Nav.Link eventKey="link-2">Outwear</Nav.Link>
				</Nav.Item>
				<Nav.Item as="li">
					<Nav.Link eventKey="link-3">Bags</Nav.Link>
				</Nav.Item>
				<Nav.Item as="li">
					<Nav.Link eventKey="link-4">Shose</Nav.Link>
				</Nav.Item>
				<Nav.Item as="li">
					<Nav.Link eventKey="link-5">Beauty</Nav.Link>
				</Nav.Item>
				<Nav.Item as="li">
					<Nav.Link eventKey="link-6">Accessories</Nav.Link>
				</Nav.Item>

				<NavDropdown className="doit" title="Dropdown" id="nav-dropdown">
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.1">Action</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.2">Another action</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.3">Something else here</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Divider />
					<NavDropdown.Item eventKey="4.4">Separated link</NavDropdown.Item>
				</NavDropdown>
				<Dropdown >
					<Dropdown.Toggle className="doit" variant="success" id="dropdown-basic">
						Dropdown Button
 					 </Dropdown.Toggle>

					<Dropdown.Menu>
						<Dropdown.Item href="#/action-1">Action</Dropdown.Item>
						<Dropdown.Item href="#/action-2">Another action</Dropdown.Item>
						<Dropdown.Item href="#/action-3">Something else</Dropdown.Item>
					</Dropdown.Menu>
				</Dropdown>
			</Nav>
		);
	}
}

export default CatagoryMenu;
